s about this article\'s proposal? which text would you use as intro?',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'2019-04-25 11:05:15','2019-05-07 19:21:34'),(477,441,434,78,'is this a technical bugs\' repository or should we post also suggestions? I\'m confused',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'2019-04-25 11:05:15','2019-04-25 23:54:54'),(478,0,434,78,'some days ago i haven\'t received any notification after having opened a project and someone commented on it. I only got them once becoming active part of the thread.\r\nbut today I was adding myself comments on the project i have opened and i didn\'t received any notification from the admin cooperacy.org account...I wonder if this is correct (this is bea writing)',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'2019-04-25 11:05:15','2019-05-30 22:02:35'),(479,467,434,78,'no more input compared to my original statement. :-)',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'2019-04-25 11:05:15','2019-04-25 23:54:54'),(480,408,401,78,'it\'s not that I want another video :-) I meant that tesla and his work can be an interesting topic for cooperacy to share, if we can find a video or an article that is more in line with our tone or our scope. I will look for it as well, but the one we have now is not aligned with cooperacy tone of voice and its kind of messages (we should spread ecosystemic awareness in human communities through cooperation science research, narratives and applications - using a multilocal, inspiring, engaging, sometimes epic with never too much grandeur tone of voice. our words are honest, positive and propositive). I hope this helps understanding my position',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'2019-04-25 11:05:15','2019-04-25 23:54:54'),(481,408,401,107,'Indeed, I proposed an alternative to this video with the article/inteview above. And Ive been searching also for a video or other writings about him...',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'2019-04-25 11:05:15','2019-04-25 23:54:54'),(482,404,401,107,'\"Consumers have high demands for companies to address food waste, but currently that does not translate to their own behaviour and it remains to be seen if the trend will go mainstream soon.\"\r\n77% of those who eat out or buy takeaways agree that restaurants should be more committed to reducing food waste, but only 17% are interested in eating dishes made from food that was due to be thrown away.',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'2019-04-25 11:05:15','2019-05-07 17:49:42'),(483,408,401,7,'What about posting the video and the  article for who wants to know more?',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'2019-04-25 11:05:15','2019-04-25 23:54:54'),(484,408,401,107,'Again, already answered. Read above',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'2019-04-25 11:05:15','2019-04-25 23:54:54'),(485,408,401,7,'The tone of voice of the video is inspiring, I don\'t see any integration in your explanations, so nobody will see neither the video nor the article :-)',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'2019-04-25 11:05:15','2019-04-25 23:54:54'),(486,408,401,78,'About the tone I have already answered, it is too angry and all the good messages are overwhelmed with bitter critics and accuses. Our tone is should be positive and propositive, together with inspiration. \r\n\r\nRegarding integration, well actually all videos/articles are still available on the platform and nothing is being deleted, so any of the members have access to them. :-) \r\nIn this specific example, I think Tesla\'s discoveries/studies are relevant for Cooperacy, as already mentioned, so I\'m absolutely welcoming the topic...but I also look for the appropriate way to deliver his messages. The article is very interesting, but a bit too long and not super narrowed to our purposes. I\'m just parking it aside as an option if I can\'t find any more fit for purpose alternative. cheers',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'2019-04-25 11:05:15','2019-04-25 23:54:54'),(487,408,401,107,'This video is interesting, but maybe a bit too long...\r\nhttps://youtu.be/NLdtVfP4fEk\r\nOtherwise I found his autobiography in English. It will be a long post but we can divide publishing in chapters from time to time. http://www.teslasautobiography.com/my_early_life.html\r\nAnd last but least, here are some selected Tesla writings: http://www.tfcbooks.com/tesla/contents.htm\r\nsome maybe a bit complex but still very interesting if you are feeling more curious...\r\nBisous',1,0,0,0,0,0,0,'2019-04-25 11:05:15','2019-04-25 23:54:54'),(488,408,401,78,'thx a billion for the support. actually after having gone through all proposed links and searched myself for shorter or sharper alternatives, the interview seems the more in line with cooperacy\'s purposes. it doesn\'t refer to tesla and edison disputes or anger, but to tesla\'s spirit as a scientist and explorer. \"Inside the Earth, there are energies of joy, peace, and love that are expressed for example through a flower that grows from the earth, food that comes out of it and everything that makes it the home of man. Ive spent years looking for ways that this energy could influence people. The beauty and aroma of roses can be used as a medicine and the suns rays as food. Life has an infinite number of forms and the duty of scientists is to find them in all forms of matter. Three things are essential in this regard. All I do is look for them. I know I will not find them, but I will not give them up.\" I still feel it is too long and not fit for all our audiences, but let\'s give it a try',1,0,0,0,0,0,0,'2019-04-25 11:05:15','2019-04-25 23:54:54'),(489,471,469,78,' una delle cose alle quali stiamo lavorando, ma per questo tipo di discussioni e di scambi di suggerimenti.\r\n\r\nper i progetti veri e propri invece nella prima fase, di pura votazione delle idee, l\'obiettivo  votare appunto l\'idea e non la persona proponente. \r\nper mi tengo come FAQ la questione della spiegazione dell\'anonimato. grazie mille...chiunque tu sia :-)',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'2019-04-25 11:05:15','2019-04-25 23:54:54'),(490,470,469,78,'ti vengono in mente altre domande?',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'2019-04-25 11:05:15','2019-04-25 23:54:54'),(491,0,401,7,'Hi everyone. So, we turned on the authors names. We are sorry not to have communicated it, but we need to